EXPECTED_LABOUR_SHARE_SP:INTERPOLATE::=
	IF_THEN_ELSE( Switch_Scenarios=1 , Exogenous_Labour_Share_SSP1 , IF_THEN_ELSE( Switch_Scenarios\
		=2, Exogenous_Labour_Share_SSP2 ,  Exogenous_Labour_Share_SSP3) )
	~	
	~	This variable projects the future share of Real_Value_Added allocated to employee \
		compensation under different scenarios beyond 2020. It reflects \
		anticipated changes in the distribution of economic output, adjusting to \
		potential shifts in income policies, labor market dynamics, or economic \
		structure. This projected share allows the model to explore how the labor \
		share of GDP might evolve under various future conditions.
		
		
		GET_DIRECT_DATA( 'scenario_parameters.xlsx' , 'economy' , \
		'SCENARIO_TIME_ECO' , 'EXPECTED_LABOUR_SHARE' )
	|

