		=2, EXPECTED_TAXES_SSP2 ,  EXPECTED_TAXES_SSP3) )
	~	M$
	~	This variable represents the expected total value of taxes less subsidies \
		on products for future scenarios beyond 2020. It is used as a monetary \
		amount rather than a percentage, providing a direct fiscal adjustment to \
		the calculation of Real_GDP. This approach allows for specific \
		scenario-based projections of fiscal policy impacts on GDP.
	|

